And only one of them mattered.</p><p><br /></p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">The Stolen Election</p><h1><strong>Chapter 8: I Had a Team</strong></h1><h2>The Myth of Isolation</h2><p>When the world ignored me, it was easy to believe I was alone. No supporters. No signatures. No staff. Just one man trying to build a party from the silence.</p><p>But that belief wasn‚Äôt quite true.
